milton.edu/collections/object/buddy-defranco-interviewed-monk-rowe-sarasota-florida-april-13-1996"}, {"speaker": "Kenny Burrell", "relation": "played with", "confidence": 1.0, "evidence": "Oscar asked me would I join the trio... I joined Oscar Peterson right after I graduated from college and stayed with him six months", "doc_title": "Kenny Burrell — Smithsonian Jazz Oral History", "collection": "si", "url": "https://amhistory.si.edu/jazz/Burrell-Kenny/Burrell_Kenny_Transcript.pdf"}, {"speaker": "Laurence Juber", "relation": "knows of", "confidence": 1.0, "evidence": "In fact the drummer, Martin Drew, was a huge Oscar Peterson fan. And eventually he became Oscar Peterson’s drummer in the U.K.", "doc_title": "Laurence Juber interviewed by Monk Rowe, Glasgow, Scotland, July 27, 2016 [interview 1 of 2]", "collection": "hamilton", "url": "https://litsdigital.hamilton.edu/collections/object/laurence-juber-interviewed-monk-rowe-glasgow-scotland-july-27-2016-interview-1-2"}, {"speaker": "Robert Glasper", "relation": "influenced by", "confidence": 1.0, "evidence": "I wanted to sound like Oscar Peterson. I loved Oscar Peterson... I transcribed solos and all these things.", "doc_title": "Robert Glasper interviewed by Greg Thomas, Clinton, New York, February 20, 2016", "collection": "hamilton", "url": "https://litsdigital.hamilton.edu/collections/object/robert-glasper-interviewed-greg-thomas-clinton-new-york-february-20-2016"}, {"speaker": "Ray Brown", "relation": "in music group with", "confidence": 1.0, "evidence": "The stint with Oscar... he must have challenged you and you challenged him and Herb", "doc_title": "Ray Brown interviewed by Monk Rowe, Scottsdale, AZ, April 16, 2000", "collection": "hamilton", "url": "https://litsdigital.hamilton.edu/collections/object/ray-brown-interviewed-monk-rowe-scottsdale-az-april-16-2000"}, {"speaker": "Schuller Gunther", "relation": "knows of", "confidence": 1.0, "evidence": "There is no mention of Oscar Peterson in the provided transcript context.", "doc_title": "Schuller Gunther — Smithsonian Jazz Oral History", "collection": "si", "url": "https://americanhistory.si.edu/sites/default/files/file-uploader/Gunther_Schuller_SI-NEA_oral_history%20new%20logo%20%282%29.pdf"}]}